---
import Button from "../ui/Button.astro";
---

<div
  class="text-wine font-display flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-2 p-3 sm:p-6 md:gap-6"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:gap-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:items-start">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-4xl sm:text-6xl">Hi, my name is Melissa!</h2>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold sm:text-2xl">
        And I am a <span class="text-petal">Software Developer</span>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img src="./me.png" alt="profile pic" class="w-30 sm:w-50" />
  </div>
  <div
    class="pixel-bg-sheet pixel-border mb-10 max-w-[650px] justify-center p-3 pl-8 pl-12 text-sm font-medium sm:text-xl"
  >
    <p>
      I am currently in my third year of Computer Engineering at the University
      of Matanzas, Cuba. I am consistently driven to learn, share my knowledge,
      and develop tools that may prove useful to fellow developers. I believe
      that good software is simple, well-documented, and solves real problems
      without unnecessary complexity.
    </p>
    <p>
      In my free time, I enjoy creating pixel art, crafting handmade items, and
      baking sweet treats. <span class="font-symbols"></span>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-20">
    <Button> Download CV </Button>
  </div>
</div>
